Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the Magic Realm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is called the Magic Realm\Nbecause it is a world that has magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flying through the sky with a broom,\Nlevitating heavy objects,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}creating something out of nothing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone can use magic at their will,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and in this world,\Nmagic is a natural part of everyday life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magic is believed to be a gift\Nbestowed by God,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and mastery of magic determines\None's social status in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a corner of this world,\Nwhere dragons flying about is ordinary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TREMBLE TREMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Within that deep, deep forest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there is one whose existence\Ndefies the natural order.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like a cream puff\Nafter pumping iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Regro Burnedead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a chic and elegant 75-year-old{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}living with my son in a forest\Nfar from other humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}REGRO BURNEDEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was quite reckless\Nin all sorts of ways in my youth,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but when you get as old as I,\Nvery little bothers you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that’s because,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}through my experiences,\NI have acquired ways to combat stress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How to combat stress...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}RRRAAWR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pops. I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}MASH BURNEDEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you rip the door off\Nits hinges to come in, Mash!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't remember\Nif I was supposed to push or pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many years have you lived here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I just kind of forced—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you ended up breaking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Pops. I'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... If you're repenting, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's always so amenable\Nafter each screwup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}RRRAAWR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turn! Turn it! Turn it!\NYou need to turn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Weird. It won't fit back in.\N- That's the wrong position!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quit with the pounding, would you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spit on the foundling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... Yeah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mash, did you finish\Ntoday's training routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been meaning to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are all of my workouts physical?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not like ordinary people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't use magic at all\Nbecause you're different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the least I can do is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. A story for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm heading out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trusting you to housesit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- Don't break the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry,\NI learned how to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Learn how to open and close\Nthe door instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Push in, or pull out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pull out! Pull out to open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you countless times before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but while I'm out, you must never\Nventure into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Mash, you’re such a good,\Namenable son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Pops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't ignore\Nthe call of an empty stomach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're still just doing stuff\Nyou can do with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seven limited cream puffs, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. I got too excited\Nand couldn't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But these don't usually bend\Njust by squeezing your hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Let me fix them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say, "fix"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Hold on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Freaky? Huh? No, wait... Um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see it anywhere on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- No way.\N- You're right. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, are you actually a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.\NThanks for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}This year's "Divine Visionary"\Nhas been determined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The one chosen as "Divine Visionary" is Rayne Ames,\Na second-year at Easton Magic Academy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}a prestigious school in the Magic Realm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}This title is awarded{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}to the student demonstrating the highest degree\Nof excellence over the school year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}In addition to promotion to nobility,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.\NMust feel good with all that talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}recipients are gifted a grant\Nof one billion lond and are further awarded{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}provisional employment at the Bureau of Magic,\Nthe highest legal organization.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have me here,\Nliving a dull life in a dull place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}He is expected to contribute greatly\Nfor the prosperity of this country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please forgive me.\NI only stole a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me more work\Nwith your petty crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta make you regret it\Nso you’ll never trouble me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? There's an unmarked brat\Nin the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what everyone\Nwas all riled up about back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I'm out, you must never\Nventure out into the city.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it was worth coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got to eat Goblin Cream Puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy, yummy, yum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you’re doing?\NI'm workin' over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}VODKA\NABV 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a proud member of the magic police,\Nprotecting ordinary folks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And do I get any thanks? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I get is bottom-barrel pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna have me\Ntake out my stress on ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a cream puff?\NI somehow feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's pitying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's half eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you give me\Na half-eaten cream puff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ya aimin' for an indirect kiss or something?\NYa love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are ya pickin' a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's basically pickin'\Na fight with this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And whatcha gonna do\Nabout my uniform? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I will wash\Nand return these clothes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now it ain't clothes!\NNot as of this moment! Thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did ya do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Terry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brad, this kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a riot over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More like, why the hell are you naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}BRAD COLEMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because this kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Must be him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}NOM NOM NOM NOM NOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unmarked brat from that report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}NOM NOM NOM NOM NOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would anyone be eating cream puffs\Nin this kind of situation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a bit of a hassle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this may be my chance\Nfor a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How may times have I told you?\NDon't go to the city on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry. I'll never go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's really broken up about it.\NIt's clear he regrets his actions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stay mad at him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's the case, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as punishment, you'll repeat\Nthis morning's training routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. And these cream puffs\Nare for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's such a good boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought a teenage son\Nwould be really passionate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}rife with arguments\Nand rebellious streaks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as you deepen your bonds\Nwith each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's so amenable,\Nthough a bit informal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I guess he's at an age\Nwhere he wants to get out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've lived here in hiding until now,\Naway from the city in this forest, for his sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now the magic police\Nhave caught wind of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must act quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the brat I saw earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes is all I need\Nwhen I put my mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to head home and eat cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Crea" a puff, a creamy puff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Mp" a creamy, creamy puff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"uff" a puff, a creamy puff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was I supposed to push or pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew and that's why\Nyou hid that brat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know why magic has flourished\Nsince the dawn of recorded history?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we aggressively rid ourselves\Nof inferior blood unable to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a necessary sacrifice\Nfor the world to go round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, those who can't use magic\Nhave no privileges.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Privilege to live, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say,\Nthey aren't supposed to live at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spill it. Where’s the brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have no idea\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheltering the unmarked\Nis a serious offense, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and hand over the brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you play nice and give us the brat,\NI'll have my bosses spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won’t.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never. I will never tell him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you do something so simple!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic is weak.\NYou can't do anything properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our bloodline has no need\Nfor failures like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can't even do something\Nas simple as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of others\Nwho can replace you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I have always been a failure of a human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You failed again!\N- I’m really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept failing\Neven after I became an adult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You messed up again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're fired!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can you keep living like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd already be dead\Nfrom embarrassment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Completely unwanted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought that's how my life would end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's the case, then I should just...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has no mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were abandoned\Nbecause you were unmarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this moment, for the first time\Nin my life, I felt like someone needed me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swore on that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we're not related by blood,\Neven if the entire world denied his existence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would always be a father to that boy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us where he is already, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You have to get away right now, Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This means\Nhe's still close by! Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it, Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- L-Let go of me!\N- Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Please let my words reach him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe it down, old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}All that matters\Nis that you're safe! Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Old man, hurry up and...\N- Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are my one and only...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run away, Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! You had some nerve\Nearlier today when...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My second shirt today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SLAP SLAP SLAP SLAP SLAP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you run, Mash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being selfish, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But since I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well send you guys to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even use magic.\NHow are you going to take me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an idiot. Brad used to be\Non the Bureau of Magic's Security Force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regular mages around here\Ndon't hold a candle to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And a magic-less chump\Nwants to take him on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He won't stand a chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over in three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That’s the spell that drove away a dragon\Nin his Bureau of Magic's Security Force days!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't think I would get to see it here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nalcom Pas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Did he...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Nalcom Pas... He just...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He slapped it down? Like, “paff”?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can magic be paff'ed just like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I drove a dragon away\Nwith that spell, you know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? There's no way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That magical energy output!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he trying to destroy\Nthis entire area?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Brad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nalcom Pas Diagorus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This brat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's killing the momentum\Nwith his knees!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a soft touch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now he's juggling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at those dribbling moves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This brat is totally\Nmaking a fool of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, I'm gonna borrow your wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What’s going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He can use magic after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ordinary magic\Nwon't even reach me anyway...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen anyone\Nuse a magic wand like that before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Threaten my family again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:20:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TREMBLE TREMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His training was only meant\Nto teach him self-defense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How is this physically possible?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either way, we're done for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we fend them off\Nfor now, in due time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a deal, Mushroom Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do what I ask, and I'll let you\Nand the old geezer slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once a year in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one exceptional student\Nis revered as one of God's chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the "Divine Visionary."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enroll in a magic school\Nand be chosen as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, if you're selected,\Nit means God has accepted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, society will accept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just want the fortune and prestige\Nthat comes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll back you up, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen to him, Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the words of someone\Nwho was an enemy until moments ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you\Nif you want to be skeptical or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you refuse, we’ll hunt you down\Nfor the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm after you,\Nthe whole country will be, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay because you're tough.\NBut what about the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A life where you can never feel at ease,\Nand unable to set foot in a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spend the rest of your life\Nbeing hunted down,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or brace yourself to die\Nand try turning the tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You got a deal.\N- Are you sane? It's a magic school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, Pops. My motivation\Nis stronger than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about motivation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to be able\Nto live in peace again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're such a good boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My son!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MY SON
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Living in peace with Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a world that won't allow\Nsomething as natural as that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've got no choice but to crush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With my fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}NEXT EPISODE\NMASH BURNEDEAD AND THE MYSTERIOUS MAZE

